Text: 'My story isn''t start yet...the story start whit the first step and end whit
  the last...maybe...

  So the life will bring sun, the death will bring moon...700 words are waiting in
  700 countries...so words are not enough for one story...and a story is not enough
  for 700 words...so let''s start now...'
